Salem S01E00 - Salem: Witches Are Real.

This episode provides background on "Salem", a supernatural drama about the 1692 witch trials in Massachusetts and the first original scripted series from WGN America. Historians, the show's creators and the cast are interviewed and footage from the show is shown.
